# Fastify API Patterns

## Layout
```
src/routes/     → thin handlers, register on app
src/services/   → business logic + Prisma calls
src/middleware/ → authenticate, requireRoles
src/plugins/    → error-handler
```

## Route template
```javascript
const schema = z.object({ nameEn: z.string().min(1) });

app.post('/api/v1/resource', async (request, reply) => {
  const parsed = schema.safeParse(request.body);
  if (!parsed.success) throw validationError('Invalid request', parsed.error.flatten());
  const result = await myService.create(parsed.data);
  return reply.status(201).send(result);
});
```

## Auth
- `await authenticate(request)` — sets `request.user` from JWT
- `requireRoles('hub_manager', 'venue_manager')` — role gate
- Terminal routes: validate `X-Terminal-ID` + `X-Terminal-Secret`

## Error response (required shape)
```json
{ "error": { "code": "INVALID_CREDENTIALS", "message": "...", "request_id": "uuid" } }
```
Use helpers from `src/utils/errors.js` and codes from `@venue-pos/shared`.

## API prefix
All REST routes under `/api/v1/`. Health at `/health` (no prefix).
